\par\pard\plain \ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Despite the many distinctions enforced by an ontological commitment, its applicability is not less general than the meta-meta-models of contemporary modelling languages. At the same time these distinctions are indispensable for modelling semantics faithfully.}
